 most european countries providing unique added value when it comes to sanitary technology and bathroom ceramics sanitary products from geberit – form and function of the highest calibre home geberit worldwide de en home products product range quality comfort and design never go out of style our sanitary products the product area sanitary systems comprises all sanitary technology found in buildings with the exception of pipelines and is divided into four product lines installation systems cisterns and mechanisms faucets and flushing systems waste fittings and trapsthe product area piping systems comprises all piping technology found in buildings for drinking water heating gas and other media and is divided into the product lines building drainage systems and supply systemsthe product area sanitary ceramics comprises all relevant sanitary equipment in the bathroom and is divided into the product lines bathroom ceramics and ceramics complementary productsthe marketspecific product range can be found on the individual geberit country pages  geberit product range installation systems installation systems how today’s bathrooms are built the installation systems from geberit offer great design freedom and flexibility they are used in renovation projects and new buildings the wide range of products includes installation systems installation elements building blocks and concealed cisterns and guarantees safe planning calculation and implementation processes for both prewall and inwall installations cisterns and mechanisms cisterns and mechanisms the standard for modern flush technology geberit flushing systems are particularly noteworthy for their clean flushing out economical water consumption attractive design customised functionalities and pleasantly quiet operation this is especially true of the geberit aquaclean shower toilets which combine hygiene and comfort with elegant design faucets and flushing systems faucets and flushing systems solutions for public spaces hygiene functional reliability and highly economical use are the most important benchmarks for this product line it includes electronic washbasin taps pneumatic and electronic flushing systems for urinals and toilets and complete urinal solutions the watersaving and energysaving systems are available in different designs waste fittings and traps waste fittings and traps clever connections that fit perfectly geberit offers maintenancefree noiseinsulated and functional drains and traps these fittings allow for simple connection and operation of bathtubs and shower trays kitchen sinks urinals and bidets as well as industrial and laboratory installations the use of highquality materials ensures safety for the entire service life of the connected sanitary appliance – even in concealed applications building drainage systems building drainage systems technology with a systematic approach geberit has a complete range of plastic pipes and fittings for building drainage systems this range includes normal soundoptimised and highly soundinsulating piping systems for pushfit connections and welding joints as well as the appropriate fire protection solutions in addition geberit pluvia offers a system that permits the efficient drainage of roofs with a large surface area supply systems supply systems everything permanently sealed geberit supply systems made of metal plastic or composite materials meet virtually every need whether in household applications or the commercial and industrial sector geberit uses triedandtested pressing technology to connect pipes and fittings while pushfit connections are also used for pipes with smaller diameters bathroom ceramics bathroom ceramics comfort functionality and design variety geberit offers ceramic appliances for wcs bidets washbasins urinals and shower trays through traditional leading national brands many of these products have been developed in collaboration with internationally renowned designers and architects such as antonio citterio bernd brohammer michael schmidt cornelia thies and many others ceramics complementary products ceramics complementary products contemporary practical and versatile most of the ceramic appliance ranges are complemented by a wide range of matching bathroom furniture made of moistureresistant material and boasting highquality surfaces innovative shower cabins and partitions along with bathtubs and shower trays made of various materials round off the product range geberit product range click here to discover our product range interactively new products from geberit – solutions without an expiry date home geberit worldwide de en home products new products new ideas spring from proven sources new geberit products  geberit’s new or nextgeneration products must first meet an extensive list of requirements before they are released on the market at the top of the list are quality and functionality closely followed by design and ease of installation every geberit product is backed by the knowledge and experience of numerous teams and accredited specialists from various disciplinesthe marketspecific product range can be found on the individual country pages geberit in your country geberit aquaclean tuma shower toiletthe shower toilet aquaclean tuma impresses thanks to its elaborate product concept and simple elegant design it is available both as a wc complete solution with a rimless wc ceramic appliance and as a wc enhancement solution that can be combined with already installed ceramic appliances the aquaclean tuma offers a range of functions such as whirlspray shower technology odour extraction warmair dryer and an ergonomically designed heatable wc seat roof drainage system geberit pluviathe well proven roof drainage system for large and very large roofs works according to the principle of negative pressure it requires fewer outlets pipes with smaller dimensions and fewer stacks than a conventional roof drainage system the two most widely installed roof outlets in europe with a discharge rate of  and  litressecond have been completely redesigned they now have a more compact design and are easier to install at the same time the entire pluvia range has been streamlined shower surface setaplanothe geberit setaplano shower surface is designed for flooreven showers and is made of a highquality solid surface material which has a smooth and warm feel and is nonslip even when wet as many components are preassembled at the factory among them the sealing foil the time required for installation is reduced considerably this shower surface is suitable for both new buildings and renovations bathroom series acantothe acanto bathroom series comprises everything that a modern bathroom has to offer nowadays washbasins in different sizes rimless wc ceramic appliances acrylic bathtubs as well as mirror cabinets tall cabinets washbasin cabinets and much more the furniture elements are made from moistureresistant materials and can be individually combined they are highly functional and offer a lot of storage space supply system geberit volexthe new geberit volex supply system combines two well established proven and economic technologies multilayer pipes and press connections volex offers a number of nifty improvements and is suitable for drinking water supply systems as well as radiator and underfloor heating systems in addition to the multilayer pipes geberit also offers flexible singlelayer pipes made from plastic geberit tap systemelectronic washbasin taps for public sanitary facilities can be slim and elegant yet still robust and safe to use with the exception of the infrared sensor all the electronic components as well as the mixer valves and power supply are housed in a function box that is installed in the prewall in an easily accessible position underneath the washbasin the modular tap system impresses thanks to its attractive priceperformance ratio facts  figures learn more about our product innovations in the magazine facts  figures  to the facts 