onal drains and traps these fittings allow for simple connection and operation of bathtubs and shower trays kitchen sinks urinals and bidets as well as industrial and laboratory installations the use of highquality materials ensures safety for the entire service life of the connected sanitary appliance – even in concealed applications building drainage systems building drainage systems technology with a systematic approach geberit has a complete range of plastic pipes and fittings for building drainage systems this range includes normal soundoptimised and highly soundinsulating piping systems for pushfit connections and welding joints as well as the appropriate fire protection solutions in addition geberit pluvia offers a system that permits the efficient drainage of roofs with a large surface area supply systems supply systems everything permanently sealed geberit supply systems made of metal plastic or composite materials meet virtually every need whether in household applications or the commercial and industrial sector geberit uses triedandtested pressing technology to connect pipes and fittings while pushfit connections are also used for pipes with smaller diameters bathroom ceramics bathroom ceramics comfort functionality and design variety geberit offers ceramic appliances for wcs bidets washbasins urinals and shower trays through traditional leading national brands many of these products have been developed in collaboration with internationally renowned designers and architects such as antonio citterio bernd brohammer michael schmidt cornelia thies and many others ceramics complementary products ceramics complementary products contemporary practical and versatile most of the ceramic appliance ranges are complemented by a wide range of matching bathroom furniture made of moistureresistant material and boasting highquality surfaces innovative shower cabins and partitions along with bathtubs and shower trays made of various materials round off the product range geberit product range click here to discover our product range interactively home geberit worldwide de en posts since           to today           all new products from geberit – solutions without an expiry date home geberit worldwide de en home products new products new ideas spring from proven sources new geberit products  geberit’s new or nextgeneration products must first meet an extensive list of requirements before they are released on the market at the top of the list are quality and functionality closely followed by design and ease of installation every geberit product is backed by the knowledge and experience of numerous teams and accredited specialists from various disciplinesthe marketspecific product range can be found on the individual country pages geberit in your country geberit aquaclean tuma shower toiletthe shower toilet aquaclean tuma impresses thanks to its elaborate product concept and simple elegant design it is available both as a wc complete solution with a rimless wc ceramic appliance and as a wc enhancement solution that can be combined with already installed ceramic appliances the aquaclean tuma offers a range of functions such as whirlspray shower technology odour extraction warmair dryer and an ergonomically designed heatable wc seat roof drainage system geberit pluviathe well proven roof drainage system for large and very large roofs works according to the principle of negative pressure it requires fewer outlets pipes with smaller dimensions and fewer stacks than a conventional roof drainage system the two most widely installed roof outlets in europe with a discharge rate of  and  litressecond have been completely redesigned they now have a more compact design and are easier to install at the same time the entire pluvia range has been streamlined shower surface setaplanothe geberit setaplano shower surface is designed for flooreven showers and is made of a highquality solid surface material which has a smooth and warm feel and is nonslip even when wet as many components are preassembled at the factory among them the sealing foil the time required for installation is reduced considerably this shower surface is suitable for both new buildings and renovations bathroom series acantothe acanto bathroom series comprises everything that a modern bathroom has to offer nowadays washbasins in different sizes rimless wc ceramic appliances acrylic bathtubs as well as mirror cabinets tall cabinets washbasin cabinets and much more the furniture elements are made from moistureresistant materials and can be individually combined they are highly functional and offer a lot of storage space supply system geberit volexthe new geberit volex supply system combines two well established proven and economic technologies multilayer pipes and press connections volex offers a number of nifty improvements and is suitable for drinking water supply systems as well as radiator and underfloor heating systems in addition to the multilayer pipes geberit also offers flexible singlelayer pipes made from plastic geberit tap systemelectronic washbasin taps for public sanitary facilities can be slim and elegant yet still robust and safe to use with the exception of the infrared sensor all the electronic components as well as the mixer valves and power supply are housed in a function box that is installed in the prewall in an easily accessible position underneath the washbasin the modular tap system impresses thanks to its attractive priceperformance ratio facts  figures learn more about our product innovations in the magazine facts  figures  to the facts  figures  geberit  wikipedia geberit from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from geberit ag jump to navigation search geberit ag type aktiengesellschaft traded as six gebn industry plumbing parts manufacturing and supplying founded  founder caspar melchior gebert headquarters rapperswiljona switzerland area served worldwide key people christian buhl ceo albert m baehny chairman revenue chf  billion  operating income chf  million  profit chf  million  total assets chf  billion end  total equity chf  billion end  number of employees  end  website wwwgeberitcom geberit german pronunciation ˈɡəbeːrɪt or ˈɡəbeːʁɪt is a swiss multinational group specialized in manufacturing and supplying sanitary parts and related systems it is a leader in its field in europe with a global presence through its subsidiaries contents  history  the beginnings  expansion  strategy  product areas  sanitary systems  piping systems  bathroom ceramics  notes and references historyedit geberit headquarters the beginningsedit in  caspar melchior gebert started a plumbing business in rapperswil switzerland in  he began to manufacture parts his toilet tank the phoenix a first made of leadcoated wood and with lead fittings particularly a flushing mechanism was revolutionary and a great success when gebert died in  his sons albert and leo took over the business in the following years the company expanded within switzerland as well as to neighboring countries and added new products pipes taps and valves in the s the company was a pioneer of plastic parts in the sanitary industry the second world war affected the company but it soon recovered and in  introduced the first allplastic toilet tank made of polyethylene expansionedit in  heinrich and klaus gebert inherited control of the company and named it geberit the company opened a distribution subsidiary and new branches in europe which besides parts also offered technical services as germany was considered a growth market the first international subsidiary was opened there in  in pfullendorf which was also going to be the site of the first factory outside switzerland since then a number of subsidiaries were created in european countries including france  and austria  the company moved from rapperswil to a larger facility in rapperswiljona and introduced a concealed tank system in the s geberit introduced more new products such as full drainage systems flushmounted systems and new components for the hygiene sector a third plant was opened in  in pottenbrunnsankt pölten austria the company also created subsidiaries in denmark belgium and the netherlands the company made an attempt to enter the american market creating a subsidiary in michigan indiana however the us presence remained insignificant for years in  the company entered the installation systems market which went on to become the most important market of the company in  the german facilities were expanded and a warehouse complex was opened at its rapperswiljona headquarters it also acquired a big german player in the installationelements market sanbloc in  it began automating its production in  it acquired a stake in fae fluid air energy joining the fresh water supply systems sector in  the facilities of pottenbrunn were expanded in  a new plant was established in lichtenstein in eastern germany to take advantage of the new markets after the end of the cold war in  the gebert family withdrew from managing the company and the first outsider was appointed ceo of the company gunter f kelm the company continued its expansion with new facilities in rapperswiljona a factory for its mepla brand in givisiez and new international subsidiaries in italy and portugal in  the geberts sold geberit to the british private equity firm doughty hanson with the new cash the company started a series of acquisitions which included italys deriplast and walking pipe italiana germanys buchler werkzeugbau ag and the united kingdoms caradon terrain ltd in  the company opened its first production plant in china in june  geberit was listed on the swx swiss exchange in july  it raised its stake in fae fluid air energy to  percent with an agreement to take full control of fae by  in  the company suffered from the weakness of the german market but soon recovered in  it acquired a majority stake in the austrian company huter vorfertigung gmbh in july of that year with the aim of strengthen its position in the american market it purchased chicago faucet at a cost of  million dollars in  it purchased the leading german metal pipe manufacturer mapress holding from lindsay goldberg  bessemer at a cost of  million euros the geberit share was included in the swiss market index smi in  in  geberit acquired the finlandbased bath and toilet firm sanitec for  billion strategyedit the company manufactures and sells its products mainly under the geberit brand although some subsidiaries brands are also used it has operations in more than  countries geberit’s strategy rests on four pillars focus on sanitary technology commitment to innovation selective geographic expansion and continuous business process optimization for a number of years now geberit has been pursuing the threestage sales model and the pushpull strategy more specifically geberit products are distributed wholesale with the company training over  plumbers and decisionmakers a year at its  training centers around the world or at external training courses to date geberit has received a range of awards for the company’s innovative strength product design and its strong focus on sustainability product areasedit sanitary systemsedit the sanitary systems area includes installation systems cisterns faucets and flushing systems waste fittings and traps piping systemsedit this includes piping inside and outside of buildings product lines are buildingdrainage systems and supply systems bathroom ceramicsedit this encompasses toiled bowls washbasins and other complementary products like furniture showers and bathtubs notes and referencesedit  a b c d e f company description geberit businessweekcom businessweek retrieved  september    a b c d e f  annual report geberit retrieved  march    staubbisang mirjam  sustainable investments strategies sustainable investing for institutional investors risk regulations and strategies john wiley  sons p  isbn    a b c d profile geberit reutersc